31 may make the requested use or disclosure;
32 (d) A description of each purpose of the requested use or disclosure, including but not limited
33 to a statement that the use or disclosure is at the request of the individual;
34 (e) An expiration date or an expiration event that relates to the individual or the purpose of the
35 use or disclosure;
